<p><strong>REVOGA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE ARTIGOS DESTE DIPLOMA:</strong> n/a</p>', null, '2009-04-20 23:51:51.116000', null, false, false, true, 22, 260, 11, 'Decreto-Lei_78_2004.pdf', null, null);
