<p><strong>REVOGA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE ARTIGOS DESTE DIPLOMA:</strong> n/a</p>', null, '2009-04-20 23:51:16.898000', '2009-05-06 10:52:56.653000', false, false, false, 22, 260, 14, 'Decreto-Lei_348_1989.pdf', null, null);
