    <li><span>Directiva n&ordm; 8/8/CE, do Parlamento Europeu e do Conselho, de 16 de Fevereiro de 1998 </span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: justify"><span style="color: #003366"><strong><span>DIPLOMAS ALTERADOS: </span></strong></span><span>n/a </span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify"><span style="color: #003366"><strong><span>DIPLOMAS REVOGADOS: </span></strong></span></p>
<ul>
