<p style="text-align: justify; "><strong>REVOGA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE ARTIGOS DESTE DIPLOMA: </strong>n/a</p>', null, '2009-04-20 23:51:52.455000', null, false, false, true, 22, 249, 11, 'Declaracao_de_Rectificacao_2_2006.pdf', null, null);
