<p><strong>REVOGA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE ARTIGOS DESTE DIPLOMA:</strong> n/a</p>', null, '2009-07-11 19:36:56.779000', null, false, false, true, 22, 260, 11, 'DL_323_2003.pdf', null, null);
