    <li>Os artigos 2.&ordm;, 4.&ordm;, 5.&ordm;, 6.&ordm;, 8.&ordm;, 11.&ordm;, 12.&ordm;, 16.&ordm; e 17.&ordm; e o anexo I do Decreto-Lei n.&ordm; 108/2010, de 13 de outubro</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: #003366"><strong>DIPLOMAS REVOGADOS:</strong></span><span style="color: #333399"><strong> </strong></span>n/a</p>
