    <li>Altera os artigos 407.&ordm;, 410.&ordm;, 412.&ordm;, 415.&ordm;, 416.&ordm;, 435.&ordm;, 436.&ordm;, 438.&ordm;, 441.&ordm;, 442.&ordm;, 447.&ordm; e 448.&ordm; da Lei n.&ordm; 35/2004, de 29 de Julho;</li>
